>>Hi.

00:03:46.620 --> 00:03:48.015 align:middle line:90%
>>Hello there.

00:03:48.015 --> 00:03:49.880 align:middle line:90%
>>Nice to see you.

00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:52.500 align:middle line:84%
>>For five years,
