00:04:03.580 --> 00:04:04.380 align:middle line:90%
>>Yes, we hear.

00:04:04.380 --> 00:04:05.255 align:middle line:90%
>>Somebody's talking.

00:04:05.255 --> 00:04:07.148 align:middle line:90%
>>Shh.

00:04:07.148 --> 00:04:07.948 align:middle line:90%
>>Hello.

00:04:07.948 --> 00:04:09.520 align:middle line:90%
[WHISPERING]

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:10.320 align:middle line:90%
>>Come on, friend.

00:04:10.320 --> 00:04:11.300 align:middle line:90%
>>Come, on friend.

00:04:11.300 --> 00:04:13.120 align:middle line:90%
>>We can hear your story.

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:16.380 align:middle line:90%
[WHISPERING]

00:04:16.380 --> 00:04:18.860 align:middle line:84%
>>But the Scole Group
went far beyond this,

00:04:18.860 --> 00:04:21.880 align:middle line:84%
