00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:07.510 align:middle line:90%
>>But a great deal did happen.

00:07:07.510 --> 00:07:10.710 align:middle line:84%
More, in fact, than any other
mediumship experiment ever

00:07:10.710 --> 00:07:12.380 align:middle line:90%
conducted.

00:07:12.380 --> 00:07:14.110 align:middle line:10%
