00:55:57.830 --> 00:56:05.460 align:middle line:90%


00:56:05.460 --> 00:56:08.900 align:middle line:84%
>>Although EVP provides some
comfort to the bereaved,

00:56:08.900 --> 00:56:12.580 align:middle line:84%
