voices are often unclear,

00:56:12.580 --> 00:56:15.395 align:middle line:84%
always one way and
frustratingly short.

00:56:15.395 --> 00:56:22.580 align:middle line:90%


00:56:22.580 --> 00:56:25.490 align:middle line:84%
>>One way that we also
