the possibility of recording

00:56:46.030 --> 00:56:46.920 align:middle line:90%
anything.

00:56:46.920 --> 00:56:49.810 align:middle line:10%
When the machine, which
contained a blank cassette,

00:56:49.810 --> 00:56:52.830 align:middle line:10%
was activated, witnesses
were astonished,

00:56:52.830 --> 00:56:55.728 align:middle line:10%
when they heard this voice
asking them a question.

00:56:55.728 --> 00:56:58.685 align:middle line:10%


00:56:58.685 --> 00:56:59.485 align:middle line:10%
>>Yes.

00:56:59.485 --> 00:57:03.884 align:middle line:90%


00:57:03.884 --> 00:57:06.369 align:middle line:10%
[LAUGHING]

00:57:06.369 --> 00:57:09.340 align:middle line:10%


00:57:09.340 --> 00:57:10.140 align:middle line:10%
>>Yes.

00:57:10.140 --> 00:57:12.270 align:middle line:10%
>>Historic moment, it is.

00:57:12.270 --> 00:57:15.130 align:middle line:84%
>>The Scole Group say that
their spirit communicators

00:57:15.130 --> 00:57:18.770 align:middle line:84%
