00:58:09.630 --> 00:58:13.470 align:middle line:90%


00:58:13.470 --> 00:58:16.340 align:middle line:84%
>>This matching set of initials
convinced the researchers

00:58:16.340 --> 00:58:19.730 align:middle line:84%
