His intention to build a
machine that could communicate

00:58:33.290 --> 00:58:36.470 align:middle line:84%
with the dead made
headlines around the world,

00:58:36.470 --> 00:58:40.440 align:middle line:84%
but he died before
being able to build it.

00:58:40.440 --> 00:58:43.000 align:middle line:10%
Is it possible that
through the Scole Group,

00:58:43.000 --> 00:58:44.550 align:middle line:10%
he finally achieved this aim?

00:58:44.550 --> 00:58:49.590 align:middle line:90%


00:58:49.590 --> 00:58:52.610 align:middle line:84%
>>My understanding
of life after death

