01:05:23.900 --> 01:05:26.120 align:middle line:90%
the table, and then disappear.

01:05:26.120 --> 01:05:27.880 align:middle line:10%
[CHATTERING]

01:05:27.880 --> 01:05:31.050 align:middle line:10%
>>As well as these amazing balls
of light, furniture in the room

01:05:31.050 --> 01:05:32.130 align:middle line:10%
began to move.

01:05:32.130 --> 01:05:34.270 align:middle line:84%
>>We had a table in the
center of the room that

01:05:34.270 --> 01:05:35.510 align:middle line:90%
had crystals on it.

01:05:35.510 --> 01:05:36.310 align:middle line:90%
>>It's moving.

01:05:36.310 --> 01:05:38.160 align:middle line:84%
>>The table is
indeed levitating.

01:05:38.160 --> 01:05:43.110 align:middle line:84%
>>The table levitated,
was turned on its side,

01:05:43.110 --> 01:05:45.766 align:middle line:90%
and began to spin very rapidly.

01:05:45.766 --> 01:05:47.462 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

01:05:47.462 --> 01:05:49.241 align:middle line:90%
The crystals never fell off.

01:05:49.241 --> 01:05:51.240 align:middle line:84%
Even if there hadn't been
crystals on the table,

01:05:51.240 --> 01:05:54.080 align:middle line:84%
it would have been impossible to
have turned the table sideways

01:05:54.080 --> 01:05:58.272 align:middle line:84%
and rotated it with the
speed at which it rotated,

01:05:58.272 --> 01:06:00.730 align:middle line:84%
and we could see this because
there were luminescent strips

01:06:00.730 --> 01:06:01.530 align:middle line:90%
on the table.

01:06:01.530 --> 01:06:04.280 align:middle line:90%


01:06:04.280 --> 01:06:07.100 align:middle line:84%
And it began to spin around
actually so rapidly it

01:06:07.100 --> 01:06:08.370 align:middle line:90%
almost looked like a pinwheel.

01:06:08.370 --> 01:06:10.640 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:06:10.640 --> 01:06:12.460 align:middle line:90%


01:06:12.460 --> 01:06:15.000 align:middle line:84%
As well as familiar
spirit communicators,

01:06:15.000 --> 01:06:18.170 align:middle line:84%
other voices, the group say
belong to dead relatives,

01:06:18.170 --> 01:06:19.665 align:middle line:90%
also attempted to communicate.

01:06:19.665 --> 01:06:22.880 align:middle line:90%


01:06:22.880 --> 01:06:24.230 align:middle line:90%
>>Someone for Shirley.

01:06:24.230 --> 01:06:25.030 align:middle line:90%
>>Yes.

01:06:25.030 --> 01:06:28.340 align:middle line:90%


01:06:28.340 --> 01:06:29.930 align:middle line:90%
Dad?

01:06:29.930 --> 01:06:31.250 align:middle line:90%
Hi, Dad.

01:06:31.250 --> 01:06:35.810 align:middle line:84%
I really do feel
that my dad came,

01:06:35.810 --> 01:06:38.504 align:middle line:84%
and he was the one who put
his hands on my shoulders.

01:06:38.504 --> 01:06:40.160 align:middle line:90%
>>Oh.

01:06:40.160 --> 01:06:42.690 align:middle line:84%
>>The way we were
situated in the room,

01:06:42.690 --> 01:06:44.940 align:middle line:84%
my chair was right
up against a wall,

01:06:44.940 --> 01:06:48.780 align:middle line:84%
and there was no way another
person could be behind me.

01:06:48.780 --> 01:06:51.540 align:middle line:84%
>>Then another hand
appeared in front of them.

01:06:51.540 --> 01:06:53.270 align:middle line:90%
But who did it belong to?

01:06:53.270 --> 01:06:54.860 align:middle line:10%
>>There was a
particular communicator

01:06:54.860 --> 01:06:59.300 align:middle line:10%
called Reg Lawrence, who was
an engineer in his lifetime,

01:06:59.300 --> 01:07:02.970 align:middle line:10%
and who became very expert at
producing voices from midair.

01:07:02.970 --> 01:07:04.650 align:middle line:90%
>>Hello, Reg.

01:07:04.650 --> 01:07:05.486 align:middle line:90%
>>Hello, Brian.

01:07:05.486 --> 01:07:07.240 align:middle line:84%
Very nice of you
to have us here.

01:07:07.240 --> 01:07:09.085 align:middle line:90%
>>He just touched my hand.

01:07:09.085 --> 01:07:09.885 align:middle line:90%
[GASPING]

01:07:09.885 --> 01:07:11.260 align:middle line:90%
>>Oh, yes.

01:07:11.260 --> 01:07:12.260 align:middle line:90%
He's stroking it.

01:07:12.260 --> 01:07:15.400 align:middle line:84%
It's slightly cold,
but it's flesh.

01:07:15.400 --> 01:07:16.970 align:middle line:90%
He's shaking my hand.

01:07:16.970 --> 01:07:17.770 align:middle line:90%
Oh, my god.

01:07:17.770 --> 01:07:20.656 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

01:07:20.656 --> 01:07:23.096 align:middle line:90%
>>Reg, you've made my year.

01:07:23.096 --> 01:07:24.516 align:middle line:90%
>>You've made mine.

01:07:24.516 --> 01:07:27.696 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

01:07:27.696 --> 01:07:28.680 align:middle line:90%


01:07:28.680 --> 01:07:30.930 align:middle line:84%
>>As usual, Lawrence
did not communicate

01:07:30.930 --> 01:07:32.320 align:middle line:90%
through the mediums.

01:07:32.320 --> 01:07:34.450 align:middle line:84%
Instead, the group
could hear his voice

01:07:34.450 --> 01:07:37.500 align:middle line:84%
projected from different
parts of the room.

01:07:37.500 --> 01:07:39.950 align:middle line:10%
>>Some of the voices were
moving around the room,

01:07:39.950 --> 01:07:44.090 align:middle line:10%
even high up in the
rafter area that somebody

01:07:44.090 --> 01:07:46.680 align:middle line:10%
would have had to climb up
on a ladder to get up there,

01:07:46.680 --> 01:07:50.230 align:middle line:10%
and there was no way
that that was happening.

01:07:50.230 --> 01:07:53.710 align:middle line:84%
The spirit team also came
to be regarded as healers

01:07:53.710 --> 01:07:54.915 align:middle line:90%
by the participants.

01:07:54.915 --> 01:07:56.700 align:middle line:10%
>>Has it gone inside
you, that light?

01:07:56.700 --> 01:07:57.930 align:middle line:90%
>>It's in my chest right now.

01:07:57.930 --> 01:08:00.221 align:middle line:84%
It was right there by my
heart, and I have a little bit

01:08:00.221 --> 01:08:01.710 align:middle line:90%
of a heart problem.

01:08:01.710 --> 01:08:05.070 align:middle line:84%
>>I was diagnosed
with cancer and a very

01:08:05.070 --> 01:08:07.220 align:middle line:90%
fast-moving, dangerous cancer.

01:08:07.220 --> 01:08:11.540 align:middle line:84%
I sat with Scole, and probably
two to three weeks later, I

01:08:11.540 --> 01:08:17.260 align:middle line:84%
had biopsies again, and they
came back completely negative.

01:08:17.260 --> 01:08:19.080 align:middle line:84%
>>All of the visitors
are attending

01:08:19.080 --> 01:08:22.500 align:middle line:84%
the LA session said
the experience changed

01:08:22.500 --> 01:08:24.720 align:middle line:90%
their lives forever.

01:08:24.720 --> 01:08:27.170 align:middle line:84%
>>When you walk out of
the room, you definitely

01:08:27.170 --> 01:08:30.090 align:middle line:84%
feel like you've been exposed
to something very extraordinary.

01:08:30.090 --> 01:08:31.815 align:middle line:90%
>>We actually saw the spirits.

01:08:31.815 --> 01:08:34.550 align:middle line:90%


01:08:34.550 --> 01:08:38.660 align:middle line:84%
And that's got to be positive
evidence for survival.

01:08:38.660 --> 01:08:43.180 align:middle line:90%
>>We do live on after death.

01:08:43.180 --> 01:08:47.380 align:middle line:84%
They certainly proved
that to us that night.

01:08:47.380 --> 01:08:51.640 align:middle line:84%
>>Being survived in Auschwitz,
and also my parents were killed

01:08:51.640 --> 01:08:54.470 align:middle line:84%
in Auschwitz, including
my 11-year-old brother,

01:08:54.470 --> 01:08:58.390 align:middle line:84%
who was killed on
arrival with my parents,

01:08:58.390 --> 01:09:01.950 align:middle line:84%
and I just cannot accept that
