01:09:01.950 --> 01:09:17.939 align:middle line:90%


01:09:17.939 --> 01:09:20.069 align:middle line:84%
>>Previously, we have
shown how experiments

01:09:20.069 --> 01:09:24.823 align:middle line:84%
at Scole and with Bacci provide
powerful evidence for life

01:09:24.823 --> 01:09:25.623 align:middle line:90%
after death.

