physical part of the crystal

01:19:51.710 --> 01:19:53.356 align:middle line:90%
had been removed.

01:19:53.356 --> 01:19:54.985 align:middle line:84%
Our bodies represent
the physical,

01:19:54.985 --> 01:20:00.230 align:middle line:84%
but the essence of
ourselves remains the same.

01:20:00.230 --> 01:20:04.430 align:middle line:84%
This, if you like,
can be termed the soul

01:20:04.430 --> 01:20:08.894 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

01:20:08.894 --> 01:20:15.342 align:middle line:90%


01:20:15.342 --> 01:20:19.200 align:middle line:84%
>>If I believe in the
possibility of life

01:20:19.200 --> 01:20:23.654 align:middle line:84%
