01:20:25.088 --> 01:20:27.590 align:middle line:90%
I just don't know, do you?

01:20:27.590 --> 01:20:30.562 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

01:20:30.562 --> 01:20:33.840 align:middle line:90%


01:20:33.840 --> 01:20:36.000 align:middle line:84%
>>I don't particularly
want to have anything other

01:20:36.000 --> 01:20:37.310 align:middle line:90%
