01:20:39.440 --> 01:20:42.810 align:middle line:84%
But I find it impossible
to be intellectually honest

01:20:42.810 --> 01:20:46.380 align:middle line:90%
and not believe in survival.

01:20:46.380 --> 01:20:49.870 align:middle line:84%
>>Tragically, during the
production of this film,

01:20:49.870 --> 01:20:51.605 align:middle line:90%
Montague Kean died.

01:20:51.605 --> 01:20:54.210 align:middle line:90%


01:20:54.210 --> 01:20:57.870 align:middle line:84%
But this gave us the opportunity
of testing whether or not

01:20:57.870 --> 01:21:01.490 align:middle line:84%
he actually got his
wish for oblivion.

01:21:01.490 --> 01:21:04.506 align:middle line:84%
